ls\">\r\n                <li>\r\n                  <div class=\"single\">                \r\n                      <div class=\"lang-csharp\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.argumentnullexception\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">ArgumentNullException</a></div>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                  <p>The <code>location</code> is <code>null</code>. You cannot pass <code>null</code>, because this parameter is treated as a path or URI.</p>\n\r\n                </li>\r\n              </ul>\r\n    \r\n          \r\n    \r\n    \r\n            <h4>Example</h4>\r\n            <p>The following example shows how to use this method to return the collection of <a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.windows.media.typeface\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">Typeface</a> objects from a font location.  </p>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-vb\" name=\"FontSnippets#FontsSnippet4\">For Each typeface As Typeface In Fonts.GetTypefaces(&quot;D:/MyFonts/&quot;)\n\t&#39; Perform action.\nNext typeface\n</code></pre><pre><code class=\"lang-cs\" name=\"FontSnippets#FontsSnippet4\">foreach (Typeface typeface in Fonts.GetTypefaces(&quot;D:/MyFonts/&quot;))\n{\n    // Perform action.\n}\n</code></pre>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n        </li>\r\n        <li class=\" enable-platform-filter\" id=\"System_Windows_Media_Fonts_GetTypefaces_System_Uri_\">\r\n    \r\n            <a id=\"System_Windows_Media_Fonts_GetTypefaces_\"></a>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n          <div class=\"memberName\">\r\n            <div class=\"lang-csharp\">GetTypefaces(Uri)</div>        \r\n          </div>\r\n    \r\n            <p>Returns a collection of <a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.windows.media.typeface\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">Typeface</a> objects from a uniform resource identifier (URI) value that represents the font location.</p>\n\r\n    \r\n            <pre class=\"memberDeclaration\"><code class=\"csharp lang-csharp\">public static System.Collections.Generic.ICollection&lt;System.Windows.Media.Typeface&gt; GetTypefac